        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">A sight draft to be paid in livestock and cash.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>Col S. F. Austin</persName></p>

<p>please pay <persName>Mr. Florence Stack</persName> or his order One hundred and five
Dols in the Manner following, (Viz) Thirty Eight and a third 
dollars in cash, and a Mule at Cash price, and Cows and Calves at
Cash price, to complete the above Sum and Charge the same to my
a/c it being the amt. due him for work on your <placeName>building</placeName>.</p>

<p><placeName>San Felipe</placeName> <date when="1828-09-30">30th of Sep 1828</date></p>

<p><persName>M. M. Battle    </persName>[Rubric]</p>

<p>[Indorsements:] Accepted to be paid as within specified</p>

<p><date when="1828-10-01">October 1, 1828</date>&#8212;</p>

<p><persName>Stephen F. Austin    </persName>[Rubric]</p>

<p>Recd on the fifteen dollars in Cash <persName>Wm Moore</persName></p>

<p>Recd Sixty dollars in cattle</p>

<p>Recd sixteen dollars and fifty cents <persName>Waller White</persName></p>

<p>Recd eight do <persName>Mr. Cooper</persName>&#8212;</p>



        </div1>
    </body>
